Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.82,0:01:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.19,0:01:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電氣燃料費是電費加瓦斯費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.52,0:01:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後還有水費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.32,0:01:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伙食費大概這麼多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.09,0:01:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有交通費、電話費跟房租
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.44,0:01:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來可以壓在七萬左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.07,0:01:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說每週六天\N每天工作四小時的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.88,0:02:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七百元多一點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.58,0:02:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，還要買參考書喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.88,0:02:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上一些雜支的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.32,0:02:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果時薪不到八百元\N會過得很辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.52,0:02:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.06,0:02:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,存款只剩下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.69,0:02:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個月就會見底了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.59,0:02:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該說\N連下個月的房租都會很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.53,0:02:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得快點找到工作才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.50,0:02:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.14,0:02:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.27,0:02:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要冷靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.04,0:02:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ是台電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.14,0:02:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只是過來看我的存摺而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.54,0:02:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.44,0:02:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸部壓在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.68,0:02:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.75,0:02:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.69,0:02:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就在辦事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.12,0:02:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.75,0:02:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.59,0:02:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不重要，時間快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.79,0:02:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要跟我一起去補習班嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.66,0:02:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.16,0:02:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.86,0:02:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在樓下等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.70,0:02:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.60,0:03:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我出門囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.14,0:03:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.51,0:03:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心，晚上我會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.91,0:03:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.04,0:03:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.81,0:03:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有這種時候不能說“ちぃ”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.61,0:03:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要說“路上小心”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.42,0:03:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路…路上小…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.96,0:03:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.86,0:03:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，當有人要出門時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.90,0:03:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就要說“路上小心”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.00,0:03:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.80,0:03:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫作秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.67,0:03:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀…樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.51,0:03:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.05,0:03:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.85,0:03:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.78,0:03:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.38,0:03:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.12,0:03:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.82,0:03:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.62,0:03:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.25,0:03:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.02,0:03:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.26,0:03:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.26,0:03:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.16,0:03:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.09,0:03:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.39,0:03:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教人這種事還真是困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的辦得到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.17,0:04:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.51,0:04:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就要開始去補習了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.51,0:04:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.75,0:04:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐今天也好漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真是溫馨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.02,0:04:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.29,0:04:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.29,0:04:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.03,0:04:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.53,0:04:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.93,0:04:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來今天會是個美好的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.93,0:04:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.54,0:04:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一早就充滿活力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.04,0:04:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.15,0:04:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.02,0:04:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從前面，從前面上車啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#03ちぃ，記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.59,0:05:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的國中生都那樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人擁有好幾台電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.06,0:05:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是這樣的話\N我就再當一次國中生好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.16,0:05:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你是怎麼認識稔的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.27,0:05:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我是在網路上認識他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.83,0:05:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在自製機的BBS上認識他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.80,0:05:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後就用郵件互相交換情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，知道些什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.11,0:05:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於你家那台電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.54,0:05:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.58,0:05:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動用了稔他家的\N四台電腦還是沒輒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.68,0:05:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後只知道她果真是自製機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.42,0:05:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及擁有學習機能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.79,0:05:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好像被安裝了什麼防火牆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.19,0:05:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以搞不懂她是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.66,0:05:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很幸運嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能撿到這麼棒的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.46,0:05:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連國分寺他家的四台電腦\N都搞不定的自製機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.93,0:05:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是很少見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.14,0:05:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後如果有什麼問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.94,0:05:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就來問我或國分寺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.91,0:05:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡我所能幫忙你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.18,0:05:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.14,0:05:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對了，你那台迷你電腦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你問得正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的花了我好多功夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.65,0:06:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天結果花了我一整晚的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.02,0:06:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻，嘿咻，嘿咻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.63,0:06:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她一直不醒過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.00,0:06:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還真不知道該怎麼辦才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.07,0:06:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.60,0:06:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼重要的絲茉茉\N我不會放她不管的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.37,0:06:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為花了不少金錢與時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.31,0:06:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,資料因為有備份\N所以倒還無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.95,0:06:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果要更換零件\N本來想去找你要的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.98,0:06:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.22,0:06:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有也要付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.32,0:06:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.22,0:06:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順便問你一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.92,0:06:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果零件壞掉\N大概要花多少錢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.76,0:06:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛，這要看零件而定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.63,0:06:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.06,0:06:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的記憶體，現在市價多少？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.70,0:06:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.71,0:06:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記憶體是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.18,0:07:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.45,0:07:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.28,0:07:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.65,0:07:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來電腦是用手寫字的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.75,0:07:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，只要連到印表機就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那幹嘛要大費周章用手寫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.19,0:07:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼跟什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，大概要花這麼多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.70,0:07:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼多錢的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.77,0:07:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道能活幾個禮拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.47,0:07:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦這玩意可是很花錢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.41,0:07:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在大概不會做這些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.58,0:07:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果迷上升級或改造的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N可是要花很多錢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不太懂是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，很麻煩就對了是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撿到可愛的電腦是不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.69,0:07:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是像我這種貧窮重考生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.49,0:07:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的有辦法養活她嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.29,0:07:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定得找到工作才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.63,0:07:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，各位同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.84,0:08:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去自己的座位吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.31,0:08:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫清水多香子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.58,0:08:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擔任的科目是\N古文、英文與數學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.32,0:08:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後這一年\N我將協助各位學習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.09,0:08:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水多香子老師啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.82,0:08:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也是個美人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.76,0:08:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在上課前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.83,0:08:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先來點個名吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.60,0:08:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點名？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡又不是小學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.60,0:08:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.64,0:08:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我非常嚮往當小學老師呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.91,0:08:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，大家提起精神回答我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.11,0:08:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從一號開始，淺丘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.15,0:08:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.55,0:08:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.18,0:08:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.85,0:08:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個老師，感覺真不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.75,0:08:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有那種小學老師的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.46,0:08:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我重讀一次小學也無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.83,0:09:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和，你要再努力一點才行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.30,0:09:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.80,0:09:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和，連這都跳不過\N就不能算是男孩子喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.94,0:09:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和，很不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.14,0:09:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.38,0:09:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.98,0:09:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.88,0:09:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.51,0:09:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.22,0:09:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你上哪去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.25,0:09:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.86,0:09:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上課時如果還是這種態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.99,0:09:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是很可惜的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.07,0:09:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（最新或傳統的兼職，網路一次搞定）\N目標一個月賺十萬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.91,0:09:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好是在附近，公寓周圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.01,0:09:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，有幾個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.92,0:09:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天之內一定要找到工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了擺脫貧窮生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.42,0:10:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及迎接光明的電腦生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要加油！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.46,0:10:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.46,0:10:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，當作沒看到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.21,0:10:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.82,0:10:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，這裡這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.95,0:10:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.62,0:10:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.62,0:10:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問一下，聽說這裡在招募人手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.89,0:10:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉，我們已經找到人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.16,0:10:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.13,0:10:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.23,0:10:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到其它地方找找看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.17,0:10:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕不氣餒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.50,0:10:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已經沒有在找人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.27,0:10:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對自己的體力很有自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.41,0:10:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.31,0:10:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我做牛做馬都無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.01,0:10:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本店只僱用女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.08,0:10:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都肯幹喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.98,0:10:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，好可愛的男孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.28,0:11:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊，要我僱用你也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不是，我走錯地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.22,0:11:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經這麼晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.79,0:11:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的社會還真是嚴苛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的不景氣是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.87,0:11:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果繼續這樣下去\N來東京就沒意義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.14,0:11:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快點找到工作的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.27,0:11:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒心情去搞電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.27,0:11:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，總之事到如今\N已經沒得挑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.58,0:11:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算不在家附近\N不管是怎樣的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天一定要找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.62,0:11:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.09,0:11:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.56,0:11:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.82,0:11:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.66,0:11:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不小心發了呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.86,0:11:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不會，別放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.00,0:11:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，這可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是不小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.87,0:11:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.04,0:11:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.17,0:11:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…真的很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.71,0:11:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.27,0:11:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來嘛，來嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.31,0:12:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.72,0:12:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你暫時先穿這件衣服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.82,0:12:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你把這些送去洗衣店洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.02,0:12:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…妳不用這麼做也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.76,0:12:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我用熨斗幫你燙乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.49,0:12:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我燙好之前\N請在這裡等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.13,0:12:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.26,0:12:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.60,0:12:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.90,0:12:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.77,0:12:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那女孩還真是可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.58,0:12:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手也很柔軟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.75,0:12:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好從初次見面的這天起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.88,0:12:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就綻放出愛的花朵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.19,0:12:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.42,0:12:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.49,0:12:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該先問她名字才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.20,0:12:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，沒人在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.27,0:12:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.90,0:13:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美，妳能來幫個忙嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.44,0:13:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.31,0:13:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉，好忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.98,0:13:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.88,0:13:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，原來是居酒屋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.89,0:13:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是電腦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.16,0:13:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，什麼事都會做耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.93,0:13:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後ちぃ也能做到這種程度嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個，我是因為被水潑到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.44,0:13:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不是什麼可疑的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.64,0:13:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我在等燙衣服時\N聽到了聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.08,0:13:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.71,0:13:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.58,0:13:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，這件衣服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.55,0:13:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，你不是在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.29,0:13:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼忙你上哪去了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.02,0:13:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快點的話\N會趕不上開店喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.26,0:13:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快，動作快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.36,0:13:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.46,0:13:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多好了，店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.44,0:14:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天，也要麻煩你囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.95,0:14:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那個新人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.68,0:14:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手腳很勤快呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.96,0:14:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，有什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.73,0:14:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.27,0:14:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，原來你跑到店裡來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.24,0:14:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.24,0:14:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.04,0:14:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.38,0:14:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的員工好像把你當成\N新來的工讀生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.48,0:14:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.19,0:14:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.32,0:14:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.99,0:14:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.92,0:15:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也潑了你一身水，真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.53,0:15:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不會，別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.26,0:15:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.83,0:15:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，你是學生嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.13,0:15:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.37,0:15:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我在唸補習班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.41,0:15:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在找打工嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.84,0:15:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.01,0:15:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過一直找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.45,0:15:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在穿的這件制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.79,0:15:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.19,0:15:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件衣服\N你有沒有興趣暫時穿下去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.53,0:15:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.80,0:15:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在問你有沒有興趣\N來這裡打工啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.07,0:15:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦，真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.44,0:15:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我這裡\N剛好有個工讀生離職了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.27,0:15:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我這個唸高中的女兒\N裕美也來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.58,0:15:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是人手實在還是不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.08,0:15:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.25,0:16:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也得早點開始賺錢才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.72,0:16:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是由我來拜託你才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.02,0:16:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說來，對雙方而言\N都是最佳時機囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.29,0:16:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.83,0:16:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意之至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.17,0:16:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，連店名都已經背起來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.67,0:16:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這家店的店名就叫作\N“樂意之至”居酒屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.11,0:16:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.28,0:16:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長，麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.18,0:16:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，馬上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.39,0:16:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.02,0:16:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是給我一份履歷表好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.26,0:16:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦，這不過是例行程序罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.13,0:16:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.50,0:16:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，今後還請多多…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.70,0:16:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.04,0:16:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.64,0:16:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來生活就沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.44,0:17:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以揮別貧窮生活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.88,0:17:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以有個充實的電腦生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.28,0:17:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興吧，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.05,0:17:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.18,0:17:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.05,0:17:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我家電腦的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.25,0:17:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，你有電腦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.46,0:17:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，雖然是撿到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.89,0:17:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？在哪裡撿到的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.59,0:17:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為很舊了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.30,0:17:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個我就不太清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.83,0:17:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，店裡好像也有電腦對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.24,0:17:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.20,0:17:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.34,0:17:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美妳也有電腦嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.21,0:17:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有，我的是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.01,0:17:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.98,0:17:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是電腦嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.55,0:17:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，這是攜帶式電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.42,0:17:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若只是些簡單的事\N靠這個就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.35,0:17:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它可以收郵件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.16,0:17:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還可以當計算機\N或輸入簡單的文件或資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.10,0:17:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的履歷表也是放在這裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.43,0:17:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽妳這麼一說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.20,0:18:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒寫過履歷表耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.17,0:18:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然有在家裡幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.58,0:18:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過到外面工作\N想起來這還是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.85,0:18:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.58,0:18:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話，要不要我來教你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻煩妳教我好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.62,0:18:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意之至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.86,0:18:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會寫嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.70,0:18:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的老家是北海道的牧場啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.93,0:18:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.70,0:18:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡只不過是土地比較寬廣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.27,0:18:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是寫你的學歷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.91,0:18:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.88,0:18:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.21,0:18:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧有妳，幫了我一個大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.25,0:18:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡，不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.32,0:18:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.69,0:18:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.02,0:18:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，本須和學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要叫我學長？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.73,0:19:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.36,0:19:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的年紀比我大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.36,0:19:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我人生的學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.27,0:19:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你是本須和學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.00,0:19:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，既然裕美都這麼說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.18,0:19:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最…最近的高中生\N都發育得這麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.35,0:19:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是E罩杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.05,0:19:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳怎麼突然說這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.49,0:19:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道我有說了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.59,0:19:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為學長一直在看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.36,0:19:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…我看妳\N並不是因為想著下流的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.93,0:19:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.90,0:19:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.86,0:19:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒有嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.57,0:19:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，如果說完全沒有\N那是騙人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.33,0:19:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我並沒打算要做那種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.84,0:19:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我到底想做什麼事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.44,0:19:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有點搞不清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.18,0:19:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，你好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.78,0:19:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂…樂意之至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.78,0:19:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是被她在耍著玩啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.12,0:19:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正工作也找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.39,0:19:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美也很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.93,0:20:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.56,0:20:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.33,0:20:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.03,0:20:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.17,0:20:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.20,0:20:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這麼高興啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.14,0:20:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.81,0:20:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是出門時的問候語句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.35,0:20:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候要說“歡迎回來”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.75,0:20:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.55,0:20:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.79,0:20:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.76,0:20:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.76,0:20:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.76,0:20:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.90,0:20:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興吧，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.43,0:20:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天找到打工的工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.90,0:20:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.54,0:20:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工的意思是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.51,0:20:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，該怎麼說才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.71,0:20:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，今後可以幫ちぃ買各種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.85,0:20:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳可以安心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.38,0:21:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，安心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.72,0:21:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.89,0:21:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳很高興吧，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.65,0:21:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高…興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.39,0:21:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興，ちぃ不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.43,0:21:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興的意思是…我想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.67,0:21:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是有這種表情的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.27,0:21:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.34,0:21:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.21,0:21:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.34,0:21:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了ちぃ，我會努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.21,0:21:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前，先吃飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.32,0:21:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是下班前店長分給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說因為我大概過得很辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.59,0:21:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，幫我拿那個來好嗎？那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.53,0:21:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.67,0:21:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“指東西”的這個動作\N不是叫作秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.44,0:21:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來得重新教她才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.27,0:21:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.74,0:21:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳聽我說，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.04,0:21:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.81,0:22:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.41,0:22:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.75,0:22:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.50,0:22:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不經意的走在熟悉的街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.67,0:22:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確會照映在眼簾中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.48,0:22:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在成群結隊前進的人群中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.56,0:22:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那顆遭到淹沒          感到膽怯的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.47,0:22:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raison d'etre像那種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.17,0:23:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raison d'etre如同那般的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.41,0:23:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡笑、沉沒、漂流\N究竟是為了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.45,0:23:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找著那把鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.25,0:23:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷的在尋找著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.35,0:23:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.66,0:23:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那扇門的鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.45,0:23:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作也找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.58,0:23:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生活費應該沒問題了，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.25,0:23:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.95,0:23:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就可以買各種東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.42,0:23:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各種東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.42,0:23:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，像是參考書\N窗簾或CD之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.46,0:23:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能買到之前一直想要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.59,0:23:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.69,0:23:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過ちぃ最需要的東西\N還是沒辦法買啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.40,0:24:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ需要的東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.10,0:24:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits下一回\N「ちぃ，買東西」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.17,0:24:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ既然是家電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.87,0:24:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望家電賣場也有賣她的內褲
